title: Rigmar Radio Karaoke Collection 28300
description:
We are back tracking a little on letters missed out on the original release between parts 21700 and 22000.  This was caused by the method I use to extract the Karaoke files back to the original CDG+MP3 format.

So 300 More songs and towards the end of this collection I will upload a plain text CSV file along with two pre made Microsoft Excel files, one sorted by song title and the 2nd sorted by Artist name so you can print song idea books for your clients.

Full details on where to find that will be given on the last torrent, when ever that is.

Rigmar Radio - Rockin' the Free World since 1967
